                android:paddingLeft="4.0dip"
                android:text="Processes and Threads: Processes and Programs, Programmer view of Processes, OS view of Processes, Threads, Case studies of Processes and Threads.\n\nScheduling: Preliminaries, Non-preemptive Scheduling Policies, Preemptive Scheduling Policies, Scheduling in Practice, Real Time Scheduling, Scheduling in Unix, Scheduling in Linux, Scheduling in Windows, Performance Analysis of Scheduling Policies. "
